HEADWORD: Convolvulaceous
<hw>Con*vol`vu*la"ceous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Convolvus</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Of, pertaining to, or
